                    <p change="#d2e380 #d2e400" xml:id="p_8.d2e164" xml:lang="en">Private URIs using the <code change="#d2e380 #d2e400" xml:id="code_7.d2e166" xml:lang="en">issn</code> prefix are pointers to ISSNs and can be dereferenced using a service provided by the Leipzig University Library. For example, <code change="#d2e380 #d2e400" xml:id="code_8.d2e168" xml:lang="en">issn:1110-8908</code> dereferences to <code change="#d2e380 #d2e400" xml:id="code_9.d2e170" xml:lang="en">http://data.ub.uni-leipzig.de/zdb/issn/1110-8908</code>.</p>
